measurements.description: Fifteen flowers and three buds on one arching inflorescence; dorsal sepal arching, chartreuse, maroon spots coalescing on margins; lateral sepals sweeping forward, maroon spots coalescing on margins; petals chartreuse, spots and blotches coalescing on margins and distal tips; lip white, blotched red on margin and tip, keel white, ciliate; column cream, spotted red-brown; substance firm; texture matte.
